node.text: Finally tried laminating my own brows and I was surprised at how easy it was! I see room for improvement on my next go at but very happy with the outcome! Brow lamination simply but is a perm for brow hairs which help them “stay up” for a fluffier look. The kit I used is more on the pricey side (I ordered it a while back) so I got a brow lamination kit from Amazon for next time!
